Etymology. This new species is named after Ryutaro Goto (Kyoto University, Japan ), whose interest in the macrofauna associated with echiurans (
Goto et al. 2011
;
Goto & Kato 2012
) led to the collection of the holotype .

Distribution. Presently known only from the Ryukyu Archipelago, Japan , and Talaud Islands, Indonesia (see map in
Fig. 8
).

